\binom{x}{i}\cdot\binom{x}{j}
\binom{x}{i+j}\binom{i+j}{i}
\binom{x}{i+j-k}\binom{i+j-k}{k}\binom{i+j-2k}{i-k},
\binom{x}{i}\cdot\binom{x}{j}=\sum_{k=0}^{i}\binom{x}{i+j-k}\binom{i+j-k}{k}\binom{i+j-2k}{i-k}.
